metadata.name: sPUNKratS #000
metadata.description:
- The craziest and crypto PUNK collection of the blockchain is here... an exclusive collection of only 100 pieces, which will be released in 4 blocks of 25 units....enjoy...

- NO IA used to create this collection

- Well here we go, the first NFT collection of a few that come, from the first message by Arpanet lo, until today the world has changed rapidly and not for the better, we are closer to 1984 than 2023.  
This collection arises from the need to express, share and combat the feeling of the END of individual FREEDOM, while watching series on NETFLIX. It is my way of fighting in this silent war. So good night and good luck everyone...

 I am not a financial advisor and it is not my intention to recommend where to invest or what to invest in. This is only art and social criticism.

attributes.value: Original idea and germ of this crazy collection...
